### Test the WhereItPlayed API

### Environment Setup
# Make sure you have these in your .env file:
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your_deepseek_api_key_here
# DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com
# PORT=3000

### 1. Test with a valid song query
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ask-llm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "musicQuery": "Talking to the Moon"
}

### 2. Test with another popular song
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ask-llm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "musicQuery": "Bohemian Rhapsody"
}

### 3. Test with Brazilian music
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ask-llm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "musicQuery": "Garota de Ipanema"
}

### 4. Test with movie soundtrack
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ask-llm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "musicQuery": "My Heart Will Go On"
}

### 5. Test with empty query (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ask-llm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "musicQuery": ""
}

### 6. Test with whitespace-only query (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ask-llm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "musicQuery": "   "
} 